CODE>.','The logline uses the following format:'=>'The logline uses the following format:','If you have a shared hosting account, keep this option disabled as you do not have any access to the server logs.'=>'If you have a shared hosting account, keep this option disabled, as you do not have any access to the server logs.','In addition to the firewall log, events can also be redirected to the syslog server (<code>LOG_USER</code> facility).'=>'In addition to the firewall log, events can also be redirected to the syslog server (<code>LOG_USER</code> facility).','Syslog'=>'Syslog','Rotated logs, if any, can be selected and viewed from the dropdown menu.'=>'Rotated logs, if any, can be selected and viewed from the dropdown menu.','By default, if will rotate the log each month or earlier, if it reaches 2 megabytes.'=>'By default, it will rotate the log each month or earlier, if it reaches two megabytes.','NinjaFirewall will rotate its log automatically on the very first day of each month. If your site is very busy, you may want to allow it to rotate the log when it reaches a certain size (MB) as well.'=>'NinjaFirewall will rotate its log automatically on the very first day of each month. If your site is very busy, you may want to allow it to rotate the log when it reaches a certain size (MB), as well.','Auto-rotate log'=>'Auto-rotate log','Brute-force attacks will still be written to the firewall log, even if you disable it.'=>'Brute-force attacks will still be written to the firewall log, even if you disable it.','You can disable/enable the firewall log from this page.'=>'You can disable/enable the firewall log from this page.','Enable firewall log'=>'Enable firewall log','The log can also be exported as a TSV (tab-separated values) text file.'=>'The log can also be exported as a TSV (tab-separated values) text file.','RULE : reference of the NinjaFirewall built-in security rule that triggered the action. A hyphen (<code>-</code>) instead of a number means it was a rule