d post/page edition attempt','Unauthenticated user'=>'Unauthenticated user','Attempt to edit a published %s (ID: %s)'=>'Attempt to edit a published %s (ID: %s)','Attempt to create a new %s'=>'Attempt to create a new %s','N/A'=>'N/A','Important: if one day you wanted to uninstall NinjaFirewall, do not forget to remove these instructions from your Openlitespeed admin dashboard <strong>before</strong> uninstalling NinjaFirewall because this installer could not do it for you.'=>'Important: if one day you wanted to uninstall NinjaFirewall, do not forget to remove these instructions from your OpenLiteSpeed admin dashboard <strong>before</strong> uninstalling NinjaFirewall, because this installer could not do it for you.','Log in to your Openlitespeed admin dashboard, click on "Virtual Host", select your domain, add the following instructions to the "php.ini Override" section in the "General" tab, and restart Openlitespeed:'=>'Log in to your OpenLiteSpeed admin dashboard, click on "Virtual Host", select your domain, add the following instructions to the "php.ini Override" section in the "General" tab, and restart OpenLiteSpeed:','The following lines of code must be added to your existing %s file:'=>'The following lines of code must be added to your existing %s file:','Please make the changes below, then click on the "Finish Installation" button.'=>'Please make the changes below, then click on the "Finish Installation" button.','Other webserver + CGI/FastCGI or PHP-FPM'=>'Other webserver + CGI/FastCGI or PHP-FPM','If this happened to you, don\'t worry: you could still run it in WordPress WAF mode. Despite being less powerful than the Full WAF mode, it offers a level of protection and performance much higher than other security plugins.'=>'If this happened to you, don\'t worry: you could still run it in WordPress WAF mode. Despite being less powerful than the Full WAF mode, it offers a level of protection and performance much higher than other security plugins.','It works on